{
  "stem": "1502.6",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Other bombs did not explode because they had a time clock, and they would explode in 10 hours, or 12 hours or whatever.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So this way, they kept them from repairing the-- the-- the railroad yards.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They came-- they came to the camp and they ordered-- no.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "First, they wanted volunteers.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "They wanted 25 volunteers, Jews, to dig out the unexploded bombs.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I did not volunteer, but they took the people with the red bands-- there were quite a few-- they ordered them be amongst that group that would go and dig up bombs.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "We did that work for about two weeks.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And the commander said, this is very dangerous work, and because you do this work, all the people that do this work will not be deported.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "We went every day.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "We were picked up by the [NON-ENGLISH], that was the air force.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Soldiers and officers from the air force took us to the places.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "They showed us where to dig, they gave us the tools, the picks, and we were digging around-- around the-- the bombs.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "There were big bombs, from 250 kilos and 500 kilos.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "We had to make a big hole all around the bomb, the-- dig out the entire bomb.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Then the-- the air force officers, engineers would come.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "They would put ropes around, and take a crane, and pull it out and detonate.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "But these bombs had live detonators, so when we were digging them, these bombs could explode at any time.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And the guards from the air force that where guarding us stayed like 500 meters away from the place where we were digging.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we were 25 and five escaped because it was very easy.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We could have all escaped.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
